text: Landmark (formerly known as Parkers-Iron Springs) is a census-designated place (CDP) in Pulaski County, Arkansas, United States. The population was 3,585 at the 2020 census. == Geography == Landmark is found at (34.609573, -92.321972). According to the United States Census Bureau, the CDP has a total area of , of which, of it is land and of it (0.78%) is water. There is a small lake, Landmark Lake. == References == Category:Census-designated places in Pulaski County, Arkansas
